        "Description": "Zachary Carlisle is dead. Just before he died, he was visited by 3 ghosts:\rThe Ghost of Christmas Past showed him a time when he had a pistol pointed at him by a bodyguard for not paying him for 3 months.\rThe Ghost of Christmas Present showed him getting poisoned by Emma Carlisle.\rThe Ghost of Christmas Yet to Come showed all of his wealth going away in an instant.\rHe sadly didn’t change his ways, so you will have to change everything back to what it was before and eliminate the wrongdoers!",
